# Deep Multi-Scale Video prediction Beyond Mean Square Error
---
* overview
  * Objective: Predict future frames on given video frame using GAN
  * Problems in previous method
      * MSE loss function makes blurry predictions
      * Convolution only account for short-range dependencies
  * method
      * Multi-scale network
      * Adversarial training
      * Image gradient difference loss(GDL)


* Multi-scale network
    * resolve short-range dependencies
![](./multiscale.png)


* Adversarial training
  * reduce MSE problem
